| Artifact | Convention |
|----------|-----------|
| Backend auth module | `ModuleBE_PasswordAuth` |
| Backend credential DB module | `ModuleBE_PasswordCredentialDB` |
| Backend login attempt module | `ModuleBE_LoginAttemptDB` |
| Backend failed login module | `ModuleBE_FailedLoginAttemptDB` |
| Frontend auth module | `ModuleFE_PasswordAuth` |
| Backend module pack | `ModulePackBE_PasswordAuth` |
| Frontend module pack | `ModulePackFE_PasswordAuth` |
| API type | `API_PasswordAuth` |
| API def constant | `ApiDef_PasswordAuth` |
| Credential entity | `DB_PasswordCredentials` |
| Login component | `Component_Login` |
| Register component | `Component_Register` |
| Change password component | `Component_ChangePassword` |
| Login blocked component | `Component_LoginBlocked` |

